{
  "stem": "18397.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 449.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came in the base where we were staying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We left for-- for Vilna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we left a guy, he was sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He told me where they went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And I had a lot of people with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had to send-- send them back to other places, where they belonged.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I took my time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I took it for-- I went over to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was the last one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I closed up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, I had trouble with other guys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You mean, with other groups?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, I had to do something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And were were-- we got from-- the-- from the-- from the commanding Lithuanian government, what we have to blow up, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we had to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did I get food?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to rob it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Take it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning they didn't want to give it to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they start.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was ashamed to show my face to [?everybody?].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I-- I used to put on handkerchief.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was ashamed, handkerchief on my face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this was in just the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I got-- I got used to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to do everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have a spoon and we didn't have a fork.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we didn't have a plate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we didn't have no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you have to get-- take it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Do you know how you take a sheep from a place where they-- they-- the sheeps, you know, the sheeps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the-- first of all it's full of garbage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, where the-- where we-- where we live, the place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we have to catch them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they're so-- and then they have to kill 'em.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then-- then we had to cut its throat.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
